@startuml
title UC-FR-05 Course Management
left to right direction

actor "Administrator" as Admin

rectangle "Academic Management System" {
  (View Courses) as View
  (Create Course) as Create
  (Edit Course) as Edit
  (Deactivate Course) as Deactivate

  (Validate Course Data) as Validate
  (Reject Course Operation) as Reject
}

Admin -- View
Admin -- Create
Admin -- Edit
Admin -- Deactivate

Create ..> Validate : <<include>>
Edit ..> Validate : <<include>>
Reject ..> Create : <<extend>>
Reject ..> Edit : <<extend>>

note right of Reject
Triggered when:
- course code not unique
- course ID not found
end note

@enduml
